{"tid":1550783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你可以哭泣，但不要洩氣。你可以悲傷，但是不要放棄。","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T03:22:16.000Z","uid":18074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5a3935cadac2a6c30c23c0af1e5430bf7aba30d9","tid":1550783,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:38:23.000Z","msg":"蔡英文2012年敗選宣言：<br />\n<br />\n今天晚上，我相信大家心裡都很難過；如果你心裡真的很難過，就讓它發洩出來。你可以哭泣，但不要洩氣。你可以悲傷，但是不要放棄。因為明天起來，我們要像過去四年一樣的勇敢，心裡充滿著希望。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cff46cebccaad12ff74ffd34193c9f2a3e7668b","tid":1550783,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:38:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e855e231eb9957818a3ab6989a350ff74d8db6aa","tid":1550783,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:39:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"89fa7493f22b68a6cef0ffc5019bfc12a24af797","tid":1550783,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:42:00.000Z","msg":"我們要堅強，我們一定要堅強，我們一定要比誰都堅強。"},{"pid":"db2b36428b1efcc8fa5ce7979b20e4872a475165","tid":1550783,"uid":128883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:45:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79e135e93ec6fa2c75d0c9418ee858f46c9a3726","tid":1550783,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:22:16.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}